{"tid":426002,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"平民朱古力奶嚟計，一定係維他奶最高汁！","createTime":"2017-10-06T08:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T17:43:33.000Z","uid":8598,"like":15,"dislike":292,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f83442df70d13b5675a8af1bd5c5fb18046803","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"開錯台，再嚟過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/163332_06f561a6d70a1e97cab6474e1f92f808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F163332_06f561a6d70a1e97cab6474e1f92f808.jpg&h=faec831e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻奶飲到落底有pat 朱古力醬，你可以拮飲筒落去前搖均佢，成包嘢飲落時滑勁多，又或者直接飲！飲到落底就一層厚厚嘅醬衝擊你嘅口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可惜無家庭裝賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢隻奶無得輸，不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da45abdcc91a5d3bf6a88985e2afea015868efa","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"有無挑戰！？"},{"pid":"4c1c027119ad481b48ce887301ec103985456b26","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"無挑戰"},{"pid":"13e47abdcffe72d4ce8482dc7f428a3d51202fe5","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"貢丸"},{"pid":"92080731b06ee5b98a12964bd3bb5831d28d584b","tid":426002,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"係好飲，不過冇牛奶陣奶油味硬係唔夠喉咁"},{"pid":"5a15bc8a8e999f12bb8c951ab8f81e31e0af5fc4","tid":426002,"uid":28832,"like":151,"dislike":2,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"朱奶屌打啦"},{"pid":"17239a8