1.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個個時鐘意飲子母奶多啲<br />\n重要係樽裝<br />\n但冇左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為唔好飲，無巿場，所以被淘汰，你認唔認同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔認同<br />\n佢重有出盒裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係細個硬係覺得樽裝好飲啲<br />\n<br />\n不過講真呢盒咁嘅濕鳩朱古力豆奶<br />\n真係朱奶都屌打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20db3c432319819f35750a6636acef80f5ab01a1","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個個時鐘意飲子母奶多啲<br />\n重要係樽裝<br />\n但冇左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為唔好飲，無巿場，所以被淘汰，你認唔認同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔認同<br />\n佢重有出盒裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係細個硬係覺得樽裝好飲啲<br />\n<br />\n不過講真呢盒咁嘅濕鳩朱古力豆奶<br />\n真係朱奶都屌打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留意吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朱奶垃圾"},{"pid":"4ede7ac36e873b51c40d84092772abbf1d9cd235","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>維記 特濃</blockquote><br />\n維記真心正</blockquote><br />\n飲吓先今晚，但我都覺應該太重口味"},{"pid":"18f43c9b1749ea132e91ae8014eca3d794b7c18d","tid":426002,"uid":25028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:02:14.000Z","msg":"維記好飲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34266a05d5bd9fb9904b44d2850c6601e3469ac5","tid":426002,"uid":38737,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:04:04.000Z","msg":"睇topic以為講朱奶<br />\n屌<br />\n差啲畀錯正皮"},{"pid":"fd3da83f0e15304056fd770d4f5d3437bc7d2bb5","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>維記好飲好多<img src=