食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e178f5002701b4981fd8f9744734aa30464eb0f2","tid":426002,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好難想像會有香港人未飲過朱奶</blockquote><br />\n做咩無端端會咁諗</blockquote><br />\n中學小食部必定有得買，早餐一定會飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fce42b7be9fa9f18d42b32ef1a80573e85c748","tid":426002,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>維記 特濃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日早餐一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家我每朝都叮一包我講嗰包撈麥皮食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撈粟米片好食d"},{"pid":"c6db303b347e627961eab1574f2fbe561bd4677b","tid":426002,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係好飲，不過冇牛奶陣奶油味硬係唔夠喉咁</blockquote><br />\n牛奶？有無相</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n維他隻朱古力奶唔係朱古力加豆奶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他十字牌，維記之類用牛奶溝<br />\n有個奶味"},{"pid":"d1ef8de2405d9b0a83eb73dcbfa6a66fa3d10501","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好難想像會有香港人未飲過朱奶</blockquote><br />\n做咩無端端會咁諗</blockquote><br />\n中學小食部必定有得買，早餐一定會飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱呀，小學嗰時就係賣維他奶，一試難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfa137d86838e415a7204fc2ad356e6424c3fdb","tid":426002,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc